Rating: 3
This rice is delicious and easy. I've made it many times before for many satisfied people. I have also adapted this recipe for use with quinoa instead of rice. Cook the quinoa in the chicken broth and drain once desired texture of quinoa is reached. Then, add onions that have been sauteed ahead of time, and mix in basil and pine nuts. A great substitue for rice.

